data.description: HUGE price adjustment! 5,098 sq ft HOME, 1,200 sq ft GUEST HOUSE, WORKSHOP, POOL/SPA! STAYCATION home includes a screened & heated pool/spa, workshop, 2 bedroom guest house w/ dry sauna, spacious 1.76 acre lot. 4/5 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, study, media room (TV, Stereo, Speakers, Recliners w/ seat shakers), game room. 50' x 50' insulated workshop w/ 16' ceilings, 12' tall & 10' wide overhead doors, stunning 1,200 sq ft guest house built in 2018 with 2 bedrooms, full bath, living room, full kitchen, laundry room, & a dry sauna. Storage above guest house (Texas Basement). High speed internet/fiber for gaming, streaming, or working from home. The Commons of Lake Houston community features a lakeside park with a boat ramp, picnic areas, fishing piers, and a community pool. Bring your RV, boat, jet ski, kayak, and swim suit and start enjoying your staycation property today. The Commons is located near the Grand Parkway (99) for easy access to the airport, shopping, and hospitals. TOUR TODAY!
